README for TreibBoje project directory.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Pre-requisites:
----------------

- for debugging and during program development the 'Streaming'
  library is used, see:
  http://arduiniana.org/libraries/streaming
- OneWire based sensors are access through the OneWire library,
  see:
  http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/td_libs_OneWire.html
- Dallas OneWire temperature sensors are accessed via
  https://github.com/milesburton/Arduino-Temperature-Control-Library
  see also:
  http://milesburton.com/Main_Page?title=Dallas_Temperature_Control_Library
- sending the data via the (12+1)-bit RCSwitch protocol requires the
  RCSwitch library, see:
  https://github.com/sui77/rc-switch
- for reading the DS1307 RTC module we are using the RTClib from Adafruit:
  https://github.com/adafruit/RTClib
- decoding the GPS messages from a NEO-6M based GPS receiver is
  done via:
  https://github.com/SlashDevin/NeoGPS

Sub-directories:
-----------------

None at the moment.

Wiring:
--------

  TX-PIN      10

  OneWire      2

  LED 1        4
  LED 2        5
  LED 3        6
  LED 4        7

 SW-Serial:

  TXD          ?
  RXD          ?

  LDR         A0 (14)
  Batt.       A1 (15)

 Builtin:

  TX0          0
  RX0          1

  SDA         A4     TWI for RTC
  SCL         A5

 SD-Card interface (Arduino Uno & Nano):

  MOSI        11
  MISO        12
  CLK         13
  CS           8    (Sparkfun SD shield)

================================================================================

